    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "これが、麻奈さんが決勝で\n歌おうとしていた歌……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the song that Mana\nwanted to sing at the finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 7.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースのみんな、琴乃ちゃんに\nお願いされなかったとしても、歌っていたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ I’m sure that everyone in Sunny Peace\nwould have sung it anyway‚ even if you hadn’t asked them to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 13.766666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。みんな絶対歌いたいって言って\n猛練習してたんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They all said they really wanted to sing it.\nAnd they practiced like crazy for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね。前に進むにしても\n麻奈様に何も捧げずに、なんてありえませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ indeed. It would be unfair for them to advance\nwithout paying tribute to Goddess Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 26.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……みんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
