      "text": "（さくらの歌が終わった）\n（聞いたこともないような大きな拍手が巻き起こる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sakura’s song ends.)\n(The audience erupts into thunderous applause‚ the likes of which I’ve never heard before.)",
